    "description": {
      "zh": "特种行动战术面罩 (SOTR) 呼吸面罩由 Gentex 公司设计制造，专门用于过滤有害气体成分与悬浮颗粒，避免使用者吸入。本品仅限陆上任务使用，可有效过滤包括铅、石棉颗粒、油性挥发物在内的大多数有害物质。",
      "en": "The SOTR respirator was developed by Gentex to protect operators from hazardous airborne compounds and particles, intended for use only in ground operations. Provides reliable filtration against most harmful particles, including lead, asbestos, lubricants, and smoke from burning materials."
    },
